            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Diet and prey selection in the Mediterranean horseshoe bat Rhinolophus euryale (Chiroptera, Rhinolophidae) during the pre-breeding season",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Urtzi",
