            "title": "Spatial variation in the diet of the Barn Owl Tyto alba in the Caribbean",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Maarten",
                    "lastName": "Flikweert"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
